<br>
Future Parents?<br>
Perhaps, have a list of awaiting parents.  They've already registered, put in their desires, and credit information.  When a mother arrives at the hospital or clinic, her future child is ran through the database.  Parents are found, and their account charged.<br>
<br>
Woman Terminating the Pregnancy?<br>
We already know that many of the women that make this decision, are not in a financially secure situation.  So they can't afford this procedure, which I'd imagine would be very expensive.<br>
<br>
Government?<br>
Well the government already supports the children given up for adoption, until the time that they are adopted out.  Seems the precidence is already present.<br>
<br>
So yeah, the government.<br>
